Package com.foreach.across.modules.web.ui.elements

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ConfigurableTextViewElement
    Interface extending a ViewElement with a settable text property.
    HtmlViewElement
    Adds base properties for a HTML node, like css class and html id support.
    HtmlViewElement.Functions
    Nested interface which contains wither functions specific for HTML view elements.
    ViewElementGenerator.CreationCallback<T,U extends ViewElement>
    Callback interface for customizing the generated ViewElement.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractNodeViewElement
    Base class for a HtmlViewElement that supports child nodes.
    AbstractTextNodeViewElement
    Base class that extends AbstractNodeViewElement with the ConfigurableTextViewElement.
    AbstractVoidNodeViewElement
    Base class for a single configurable node that supports attributes but no child nodes.
    ContainerViewElement
    A container is a named collection of elements (ContainerViewElement.getChildren() that allows configuration of a custom template for rendering.
    HtmlViewElements
    Contains factory methods and ViewElement.Wither functions for HTML5 nodes.
    NodeViewElement
    Represents a generic node (html element).
    TemplateViewElement
    A ViewElement that simply renders as a custom template.
    TextViewElement
    A simple text item.
    ViewElementGenerator<ITEM,VIEW_ELEMENT extends ViewElement>
    Represents a collection of ViewElement instances that are generated based on a template or callback method and an input item.
    VoidNodeViewElement
    A void node is a node that has attributes but contains no children.
